com.phunware.core

Class PwLog

  • com.phunware.core.PwLog

  • public class PwLog

    Show logs for the MaaS SDKs. Logs are turned off by default. To turn logs on, call PwLog.setShowLog with a true parameter.

    See Also:
    PwLog.setShowLog
